name: editdistance-s
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "editdistance-s" %}
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/editdistance_s-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a2ea53a4f7c2fcf151ba0f35c8a258771912ba0b4068011bb76aa55a79187941

build:
  number: 3
  skip: True  # [py<36]
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cffi                                   # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:
    - cffi >=1
    - pip
    - python
    - wheel
  run:
    - cffi >=1
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - editdistance_s
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://www.github.com/asottile/editdistance-s
  summary: Fast implementation of the edit distance (Levenshtein distance)
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - nicoddemus
